From 63c9103009dec797aca4f9399bf241bff8f008a1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Girish Kumar M P <gmp@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Jul 2025 11:47:34 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:mac80211:Add per-TID TX stats support with drop
 reasons

Improve the TX statistics reporting in the mac80211 subsystem by adding
detailed counters for various TX packet reasons and drop statistics for
specific TIDs.

Patch-dependency:none

Signed-off-by: Girish Kumar M P <gmp@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
